<a href="https://hu.ma.ne/">Humane Unveils AI&#160;Pin</a>&nbsp;<a class="permalink" title="Permanent link to ‘Humane Unveils AI Pin’" href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2023/11/09/humane-ai-pin">&#9733;</a>
</dt>
<dd>
<p>10-minute intro video from Humane co-founders Imran Chaudhri and Bethany Bongiorno. Really curious to see reviews of this. They really do mean for this to replace, not supplement, your phone.</p>

