<dt>
<a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2023/11/05/trump-revenge-second-term/">Trump’s Dark Plans for a Second Term</a>&nbsp;<a class="permalink" title="Permanent link to ‘Trump’s Dark Plans for a Second Term’" href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2023/11/07/trump-dark-plans">&#9733;</a>
