is an ongoing menace to the entire democratic order of the United 
States. [...] </p>

<p>The coalition of prodemocracy voters — I am one of them — is 
shocked at the relative lack of outrage when Trump says hideous 
things. (The media’s complacency is a big part of this problem, 
