<dd>
<p>Strong, tight, 45-minute keynote. Highlights:</p>

<ul>
<li>Their next-generation model, <a href="https://openai.com/blog/new-models-and-developer-products-announced-at-devday">GPT-4 Turbo</a>, which is both smarter and cheaper to use than GPT-4.</li>
<li>“<a href="https://openai.com/blog/introducing-gpts">GPTs</a>”, their name for no-code custom AI agents. There are an awful lot of AI startups whose entire purposed seemed to be just this.</li>
</ul>

<p>Really enjoyed seeing live demos on stage, and Sam Altman came across well. Smart, engaged, and honest. Worth watching.</p>

</dd>


