<a href="https://daringfireball.net/thetalkshow/2023/10/27/ep-387">The Talk Show: ‘Are There Ever Too Many Love Songs?’</a>&nbsp;<a class="permalink" title="Permanent link to ‘The Talk Show: ‘Are There Ever Too Many Love Songs?’’" href="https://daringfireball.net/linked/2023/10/27/the-talk-show-387">&#9733;</a>
